            <h1>Solar Project Management Tool</h1>
            <p>Our Solar Project Management Tool is a comprehensive software solution that connects sales reps, construction crews, operations managers, and end-customers to manage every aspect of a solar installation project's lifecycle.</p>
            <p>Our tool includes the following features to fully support each installation project:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Instant communications</li>
                <li>Photo and image taking and documentation</li>
                <li>Project management tools</li>
                <li>CRM (Customer Relationship Management) tools</li>
                <li>Document organization</li>
                <li>Financial tools with payment installment tracking</li>
                <li>Multi-portal interface with controlled access to different functionalities and shared data</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Our tool is designed to be used by staff involved in day-to-day solar EPC business, including sales reps, operations managers, boots on the ground teams, site surveyors, construction managers, engineering/permitting teams, closeout departments, and residential and commercial consumers.</p>
            <p>With our Solar Project Management Tool, you can easily manage each project's lifecycle from contracts signed to post-install inspections and permission to operate from the utility. Our tool provides KPI tracking functionality for each typical solar EPC project stage, including initial notice to proceed from the bank for funding, interconnection management, and procurement/equipment logistics.</p>
            <p>Ready to streamline your solar project management process? Sign in to our tool using the appropriate login above or contact us for more information.</p>
